ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce27e6bab47862ebe53ec0cb92df9fa3dc44f17","tid":680072,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9240601a3a98c915c7bcd4420b748c9d7c00440","tid":680072,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"好似香港難啲有平嘅地方踩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：算係初學 喺馬路有次p得好甘，好彩冇大礙，但同我一齊踩嗰個fd出國深造唔再返所以暫時冇再踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"初學係咪要買頭盔個d保護下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73b1e7add78800f6dcf3148cf16f462e8a1e5f1","tid":680072,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce27e6bab47862ebe53ec0cb92df9fa3dc44f17","tid":680072,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9240601a3a98c915c7bcd4420b748c9d7c00440","tid":680072,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"好似香港難啲有平嘅地方踩？<br />\n<br />\n利申：算係初學 喺馬路有次p得好甘，好彩冇大礙，但同我一齊踩嗰個fd出國深造唔再返所以暫時冇再踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"初學係咪要買頭盔個d保護下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"睇你踩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n我諗平路冇乜嘢<br />\n我有買頭盔同護具，但嗰時未到貨，結果出事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起都驚<br />\n<br />\n個人建議至少有頭盔<br />\n你上taobao易買到"},{"pid":"5e4feb267aebcde7f40a2ec0129fe834deb73c13","tid":680072,"uid":216717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"可能係香港第一個最大型既板聚 <br />\n希望今個星期日會見到有踩longboard既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg：docksessionhk<br />\nFacebook: DockSession Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1st DockSession in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDockSession是一個活躍於國際的長板活動組織，我們香港有幸於今年參與其中，並邀請到DockSession聖地牙哥地區代表 @joiskwan 參與這次的長板盛事。<br />\n屆時活動將會有Best Freestyle Lines, Best Tricks等比賽，贏得比賽的朋友可獲豐富的獎品！<br />\n比賽完後更有一些團體小遊戲，讓踩長板的朋友們互相認識及有一個愉快和歡樂的聚會。<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情如下：<br />\n2018年10月21日<br />\n下午3時正<br />\n西九龍文化區大馬路 ※參加者請注意安全，穿戴護具。如有任何損傷，本會概不負責<br />\n※如天氣惡劣，本會或考慮另作安排，請留意Facebook及Instagram專頁最新動態<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bo8YC-Fl6bi/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1pdit0hlmmkk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBo8YC-Fl6bi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D1pdit0hlmmkk4&d=KxW99cBNl%2FdTz7tN9B779U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cb6f0a75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBo8YC-Fl6bi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D1pdit0hlmmkk4&h=9216ef3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bo8YC-Fl6bi/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1pdit0hlmmkk4</a>"}]}